🚧 Cursor Rule: Dependency Registration (MANDATORY)
🔒 Core Rule

Every Repository, UseCase, and Bloc MUST be registered inside:

lib/src/di/register_module.dart
📦 What MUST be Registered
1. Repositories
Interface → in lib/src/domain/repository
Implementation → in lib/src/data/repository
✅ Registration:
@lazySingleton
CounterRepository counterRepository(Dio dio) =>
    CounterRepositoryImpl(dio);
2. Use Cases
Location:
lib/src/domain/use_case/
✅ Registration:
@factoryMethod
CreateGroupUseCase createGroupUseCase(
  GroupsRepository repository,
) =>
    CreateGroupUseCase(repository);
3. Blocs
Location:
lib/src/presentation/<feature>/bloc/
✅ Registration:
@factoryMethod
CreateGroupBloc createGroupBloc(
  CreateGroupUseCase createGroupUseCase,
) =>
    CreateGroupBloc(createGroupUseCase);
🔥 Strict Rules (No Exceptions)
❌ No direct instantiation using new or constructors in UI
❌ No BlocProvider(create: ...) with manual Bloc construction
❌ No repository or use case used without DI
❌ No missing registration (build must fail if missing)
🧠 Naming Convention
Type	Annotation
Repository	@lazySingleton
UseCase	@factoryMethod
Bloc	@factoryMethod
Dio / shared services	@lazySingleton
🔄 Injection Flow
Screen
  ↓
Bloc (injected via di<Bloc>())
  ↓
UseCase (injected)
  ↓
Repository (injected)
⚙️ Required Build Step

After adding anything new:

dart run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs
🧩 Example Full Flow
Register Module
@module
abstract class RegisterModule {
  @lazySingleton
  Dio dio() => DioClient.create();

  @lazySingleton
  GroupsRepository groupsRepository(Dio dio) =>
      GroupsRepositoryImpl(dio);

  @factoryMethod
  CreateGroupUseCase createGroupUseCase(GroupsRepository repo) =>
      CreateGroupUseCase(repo);

  @factoryMethod
  CreateGroupBloc createGroupBloc(CreateGroupUseCase useCase) =>
      CreateGroupBloc(useCase);
}
✅ Final Cursor Enforcement Rule

When creating any feature:

MUST register Repository, UseCase, and Bloc in register_module.dart
MUST use @lazySingleton for repositories and shared services
MUST use @factoryMethod for use cases and blocs
MUST NOT instantiate dependencies manually anywhere else
